data.description: Beautiful Colonial home nestled at the end of a cul de sac on scenic 2 acre open wooded lot. This home features hardwood floors throughout. Remodeled kitchen with granite counters and newer appliances Newer energy efficient woodburning stove. Newer roof. Rebuilt Trex deck overlooking level backyard, backing to wooded privacy. Full finished basement with huge Rec Room, Media Room and Exercise room. Rebuilt boiler and newer hot water heating system. Many additional upgrades including , new slider doors to deck and new tile floor in hallway. 1st floor office or bedroom option.   Professionally landscaped and deer proof garden in backyard. Ideal for play or entertaining
